4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper discusses quantization effects on distance measurements, which involves numerical analysis techniques. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the use of quantizers, which involves the design and implementation of algorithms for data compression.
